data.description: Check out this 3-bedroom, 2-bath home in popular Russet Woods. This home has an open floor plan and a cozy living room fireplace. The deck is just off the kitchen and overlooks a wooded area. The finished area of the basement features three separate bonus rooms. There is also an adorable playhouse outside, which the current owners use for storage. This home has a secluded feel. Schedule your showing today!
